commit_message: new scripts and lib for busco5
busco exec script is updated to the latest ver of BUSCO5
new scripts for BUSCO analysis added
new lib to manipulate exonerate outputs
bug fix: wrong calculation in minus strands
qsub_lastz_batch.rb: new parameters in lastz exec
new scripts to build target-based pairwise alignment from synteny blocks
improved: net_to_jbbed.rb. Nested fills can be reported.
custom_gff_to_getseq created and cdsgff2bed12.rb was moved under the dir
New: cdsgff2bed12.rb -- convert exonerate gff output to bed12
several scripts of EVM processing were added.
app/EVM/pipeline_1 was created and pipeline scripts added
gene_prediction_performance_evaluation dir is created and gmodels_hit_coverage.rb was moved under it
gmodels_hit_coverage.rb: query side statistics will be generated
app dir added. jbrowse dir added under it
split_fata.rb: default output dir is set as fasta_split; generate_jobs.rb: default conf file set.
converters dir was created. exonerate output converters were imported
